The identifier used in the proof to identify the claim entry is a uuid that is used in the wallet to identify the claim. This means that the verifier has a unique identifier for the claim that will be reused for every proof that uses the claim. This will allow the verifier to track the claim as it is used.

 

ex: (generated from the same code in indy-sdk)

wallet key:

